    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "TIMETABLE\nEFFECTIVE FEBRUARY 12, 2004\nAkron-Canton, OH / Atlanta, GA\nBaltimore-Washington, MD-DC / Bloomington-Normal, IL\nBoston, MA / Buffalo-Niagara, NY\nChicago, IL / Dallas-Ft. Worth, TX / Dayton, OH / Denver, CO\nFlint, MI / Ft. Lauderdale, FL / Ft. Myers, FL\nGrand Bahama Island, Bahamas\nGreensboro-High Point-Winston-Salem, NC\nGulfport-Biloxi, MS / Houston, TX / Jacksonville, FL\nKansas City, KS-MO / Las Vegas, NV / Los Angeles, CA\nMemphis, TN / Miami, FL / Milwaukee, WI\nMinneapolis-St. Paul, MN / Moline-Quad Cities, IL-IA\nMyrtle Beach, SC / New Orleans, LA / New York, NY\nNewark, NJ / Newport News-Williamsburg, VA\nOrlando, FL / Pensacola-Gulf Coast, FL / Philadelphia, PA\nPittsburgh, PA / Raleigh-Durham, NC / Rochester, NY\nSan Francisco, CA / Savannah-Hilton Head, GA-SC\nTallahassee, FL / Tampa, FL\nWashington, DC / West Palm Beach, FL / Wichita, KS\nFor reservations, book at airtran.com\n(America Online Keyword: AirIran),\ncontact your travel agent or call 1-800-AIR-TRAN.\nIn Atlanta, call 770-994-8258. En español, 1-877-581-9842.\n©AirTran Airways 2004\nAirTran\nAIRWAYS",
      "FASTER\nFREE\nFLIGHTS.\nTHE AIRTRAN AIRWAYS A-PLUS VISA.\nThe fastest free ticket just got easier. Start\nearning your free ticket right away. Pick up an\napplication in the gate area, fill one out at\nairtranvisa.com, or call 1-866-389-7877.\n9461. 1912,\n5679\nVISA\n©AirTran Airways 2004\nNYSE."
